{
  "texts": [
    "Annotations can be posted through a separate end point, which accepts json serialized versions of annotations.",
    "Annotations are then validated against the schema using marshmallow, and the SQLalchemy model is dynamically generated by the schema library.",
    "Annotations are then inserted into the PostgreSQL database after associating a creation timestamp to the annotation.",
    "After insertion, the annotation service sends a notification to the Materialization service to trigger supervoxel lookups for the recently added annotations.",
    "Deletion is implemented virtually by marking the timestamp of deletion to enable point-in-time consistent querying."
  ]
}